# 06 - Essay Writer
# Write a structured essay on any topic

NAME essay-writer
INPUT topic
INPUT style DEFAULT "academic"
INPUT word_count DEFAULT 1000

GOAL outline "Create brief outline: thesis + 3 main points + conclusion. No more than 10 bullets."
GOAL draft "Write $word_count-word $style essay on $topic. Stay within word limit."
GOAL polish "Quick review for clarity and grammar. No rewrites, just fixes. Save to essay-output.md."

RUN write USING outline, draft, polish
